NK015(ba)010:0: zhi ba'i lhan thabs dbu'i gzigs phyogs so //
NK015(ba)010:2: byed pa rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor gtso //
NK015(ba)010:3: rang snang yul du mos byas nas //
NK015(ba)010:4: rin chen d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:5: zhal gdams lhan thabs brjod par bya //
NK015(ba)010:6: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK015(ba)010:7: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK015(ba)010:8: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK015(ba)010:9: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK015(ba)010:10: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)010:11: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK015(ba)010:12: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK015(ba)010:13: skyes pa nyid na'ang skye ba med //
NK015(ba)010:14: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)010:15: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK015(ba)010:20: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)010:21: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK015(ba)010:22: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK015(ba)010:23: gnas pa nyid na'ang gnas pa med //
NK015(ba)010:24: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)010:25: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK015(ba)010:26: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK015(ba)010:27: dmigs pa nyid na'ang dmigs pa med //
NK015(ba)010:28: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK015(ba)010:29: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK015(ba)010:34: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med par //
NK015(ba)010:35: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK015(ba)010:36: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK015(ba)010:37: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK015(ba)010:38: de la rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK015(ba)010:39: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK015(ba)010:40: a rab tu brtan gyur a dkar las //
NK015(ba)010:41: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spro //
NK015(ba)010:42: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK015(ba)010:45: / 'di ni rdo rje'i dngos grub kyi //
NK015(ba)010:46: rten 'byung ye shes rgyu yin te //
NK015(ba)010:47: de la dbang chen dkyil 'khor bsgom /
NK015(ba)010:48: b+h+r+aum 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NK015(ba)010:49: gru chad bzhis brgyan par 'khyams dang //
NK015(ba)010:50: kun tu gru bzhi sgo khyud ldan //
NK015(ba)010:51: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK015(ba)010:52: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK015(ba)010:53: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK015(ba)010:54: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK015(ba)010:55: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK015(ba)010:56: a dang k+sha yi khyad par las //
NK015(ba)010:57: yi ge bzhi bcu byung ba ste /
NK015(ba)010:60: sems can ngag gi sgrib pa sbyang //
NK015(ba)010:61: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK015(ba)010:62: thugs mtshan bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur /
NK015(ba)010:65: sems can yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK015(ba)010:66: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK015(ba)010:67: phra mo bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur /
NK015(ba)010:70: sems can lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK015(ba)010:71: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK015(ba)010:72: yongs rdzogs bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur //
NK015(ba)010:73: mnyen lcug 'khril lde ma gzhon tshul can //
NK015(ba)010:74: gsal 'tsher lhun sdug gzi byin ldan /
NK015(ba)010:79: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yi //
NK015(ba)010:80: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK015(ba)010:81: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:82: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:83: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:84: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:85: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:88: gzugs kyi phung po'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:89: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:90: rnam snang yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:91: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:92: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:95: tshor ba chu'i ngo bo nyid /
NK015(ba)010:96: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:97: rin 'byung yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:98: ting 'dzin yon tan dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:99: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:102: 'du shes me yi ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:103: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:104: snang mtha' yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:105: ting 'dzin gsung gi dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:106: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:109: 'du byed rlung gi ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:110: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:111: don grub yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:112: ting 'dzin phrin las dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:113: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:116: mig shes gzugs kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:117: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:118: sa snying yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:119: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:120: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:122: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+aam /
NK015(ba)010:123: rna shes sgra yi ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:124: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:125: phyag rdor yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:126: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:127: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:128: dz+rim ku ru p+aa ni h+r+ai /
NK015(ba)010:129: a nirti r+aa ga ya mi /
NK015(ba)010:130: sna shes dri yi ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:131: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:132: nam snying yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:133: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:134: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:136: t+r+aam ma l+ye sa ma ya ho /
NK015(ba)010:137: lce shes ro'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:138: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:139: spyan gzigs yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:140: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:141: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:142: h+r+aihha h'u pad+ma bra da ma /
NK015(ba)010:144: mig dbang 'das pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:145: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:146: byams pa yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:147: ting 'dzin sems dpa' dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:148: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:149: mee d+hi ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)010:150: dza d+hu sh+pe pra we sha ya +aa /

NK015(ba)010:152: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //

NK015(ba)010:155: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:156: th+l+him sa ram pa ye s+w+aa h+aa /

NK015(ba)010:159: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //

NK015(ba)010:163: h'u swa r+aa ra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)010:164: b+aam d+hi pam su ki ni /
NK015(ba)010:165: lce dbang phyis 'byung ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:166: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i /
NK015(ba)010:168: / 'jam dpal yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:169: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:170: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:171: m+aum sh+r+ai a ram g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)010:173: yid ni rang rig ma skyes thugs //
NK015(ba)010:174: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:175: kun bzang yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:176: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:177: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:178: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK015(ba)010:179: a a a badz+ra b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK015(ba)010:180: nga rgyal lha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:181: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:182: lha dbang brgya byin rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:183: ting 'dzin sprul par dbang bskur bas //
NK015(ba)010:184: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:186: phrag dog lha min ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:187: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:188: thag bzang ris kyi rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:189: ting 'dzin sprul par dbang bskur bas //
NK015(ba)010:190: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:193: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:194: sh+aakya thub pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:195: ting 'dzin sprul par dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:196: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:197: mu ne h'u trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)010:198: gti mug byol song ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:199: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:200: seng ge dam brtan rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:201: ting 'dzin sprul par dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:202: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:204: ser sna yi dwags ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:205: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:206: kha 'bar ma yi rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:207: ting 'dzin sprul par dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:208: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:210: zhe sdang dmyal ba'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:211: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:212: chos kyi rgyal po'i rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)010:213: ting 'dzin sprul par dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:214: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /

NK015(ba)010:222: badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa li ni h'u phata /

NK015(ba)010:228: h'u pradz+ny+aan+ta krita phata rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro ta shwa ri dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK015(ba)010:229: lus dbang bdag lta'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:230: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //

NK015(ba)010:233: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:235: pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK015(ba)010:236: reg shes mtshan ma'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)010:237: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)010:238: bdud rtsi yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)010:239: ting 'dzin khro bor dbang bskur nas //
NK015(ba)010:240: dngos grub ma lus 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)010:242: karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK015(ba)010:243: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor du //
NK015(ba)010:244: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nyid la bsdu h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK015(ba)010:246: chos kyi dbyings su thim par gyur /
NK015(ba)010:248: bdag gi ro mchog chen po yi //
NK015(ba)010:249: phyag rgya chen po gsal gyur nas //
NK015(ba)010:250: spyod lam kun tu ma nyams par //
NK015(ba)010:251: bdag nyid rgyun tu brtan par bsgom //
NK015(ba)010:252: rgyud dang rgya gzhung bsgrub thabs la brten nas //
NK015(ba)010:253: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK015(ba)010:254: cho ga'i kha bskong b+hu d+ha badz+rasa sbyar //
NK015(ba)010:255: dge bas bdag gzhan 'khor lo'i sa thob shog //
NK015(ba)010:256: ces pa 'di ni bdag b+hu d+ha badz+rasa rang gzhan gyi rmongs pa sel ba'i ched du /
NK015(ba)010:257: mngon par rtogs pa'i kha bskong lhan thabs su /
NK015(ba)010:258: kahthoga ri khrod du sbyar ba dge legs su gyur /
NK015(ba)010:259: gzhung gi bar mtshams su sbyar dgos pa mchan dang bla ma'i zhal ras shes par gyis shig //
